Enhancement: Introduce a remove license button in WebUI

Before this PR, it was not possible, to remove any ownCloud license.
This lead to an issue if someone enters an invalid license, a permanent
message indicator was shown in the WebUI.
With this PR it is possible to remove the license.

https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/38843
https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/38844
